channel.title: Has anyone bought a VPS from Selfinger before?
channel.description:
[url=http://www.selfinger.com/budget-ddos-protected-windows-xp-seo-vps.html]Click me[/url].
They've apparently been around since 1999, but I can't seem to find any reviews or anything about them.
Lots of websites only show the whois about them, and nothing more. [url=http://www.scamadviser.com/is-selfinger.com-a-fake-site.html]Scamadviser[/url] says it's a trusted website, but this is the only site I've seen give any form of feedback about this company.
All in all, they seem to offer a good deal on a protected vps.
